{"tid":109533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞幫侵元朗「小印尼」 打劫非禮搞亂治安","createTime":"2017-02-06T04:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T07:44:01.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1449ae3a9c760d9f77f4e4343a3e1161bc36bb08","tid":109533,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:40:45.000Z","msg":"元朗擊壤路足球場是區內印傭假日的聚腳點，近月有南亞裔和酷刑聲請申請者大舉遷入元朗，《東周刊》記者發現，球場內有南亞裔男子涉疑非禮女傭，還想搶其財物，令這「小印尼」變成「九反之地」。<br />\n<br />\n        每逢假日，元朗廣場旁的擊壤路足球場滿是區內打工的印傭，恍如「小印尼」，她們聚集野餐、嬉戲或睡覺。突然一班南亞裔男子前來，並不時注視球場內的女傭。未幾，一名操印尼語的男子疑飲醉酒，步履蹣跚走近球場，上下打量一位穿短褲的女傭，再伸手摸其大髀，惹來女傭怒視，他無癮地轉移陣地。不久，他又涉嫌「鹹豬手」一名長裙女傭的臀部，被破口大罵，他即用印尼語道歉，笑着舉高雙手示意並非故意。記者詢問被「鹹豬手」的女傭是否要報警，她們均拒絕，說不想影響工作。另外，一群南亞裔男子徘徊球場四周，向女傭搭訕，索取對方電話號碼，又借故搭膊頭、掃背。<br />\n<br />\n印傭Kitty來港工作一年，逾三星期前，她被一名巴基斯坦男子摸胸，更想搶她的手袋，附近的涼茶舖老闆馬上通知警察，但警員只問幾句便放人，當事情沒發生過般。她無奈地說：「附近只有這個公園適合我們聚會，每程車費只需五元，若去維園來回車費要五十元，再計食飯錢，實在負擔不起。」<br />\n<br />\n        眼見同鄉被欺負，印尼華僑李婆婆上月發起聯署促警方正視問題，至今收集近二百位印傭簽名，包括多位受害人，「好多女仔怕要請假認人上庭，就算蝕底左都唔敢報警。」逾七十歲的李婆婆，曾多次被這班男子搶手袋和非禮，先後報案四次，但都無下文。<br />\n<br />\n        元朗區議員周永勤指，約四年前元朗開始聚集大批外籍和南亞裔男子，多數來自巴基斯坦、非洲和尼泊爾的酷刑聲請申請者，近月人數明顯增加，由於他們持「行街紙」，在港等候申請結果期間不能工作，只靠二千至三千元津貼維生，部份人涉嫌在區內招搖撞騙。他批評，警方漠視問題，受害人報警後，警方均草草了事，令惡霸有恃無恐。<br />\n<br />\n        警方資料顯示，今年該足球場僅接獲兩宗盜竊以及傷人、嚴重毆打案。警方發言人解釋，曾聯絡李婆婆，但對方拒絕提供進一步資料，未能繼續跟進，又強調重視所有舉報，並加強巡邏。"},{"pid":"b3c15086ec4cb19285bbf311cb44bcc425572e39","tid":109533,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160310/photo/bkn-20160310163641471-0310_00822_001_01b.jpg?20160310173809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160310%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160310163641471-0310_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20160310173809&h=6f56a9ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b20a9adffd827b3bba39c88d72a38a0295298d7","tid":109533,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"七十歲都唔放過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2aecd1432f22093013557c48cd2ab9d333938f","tid":109533,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"受害人報警後，警方均草草了事，令惡霸有恃無恐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd29226b2cb5c6853813ad0e182f03cc01bfaef0","tid":109533,"uid":23364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"又要召喚條垃圾ust南狗"},{"pid":"bce076becb964424ac21f9eac01c7e8c4fc11b14","tid":109533,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1908bf0014a71110d7d4d6dcf12720e9da8039","tid":109533,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"大家都係真主的信徒,相煎何太急? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a92a05f852758c74f1e2715cf5d6fd95429070","tid":109533,"uid":8168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"逾七十歲的李婆婆，曾多次被這班男子搶手袋和<span style=\"color: red;\">非禮</span><br />\n<br />\n南亞真識食.."},{"pid":"9711cdb686a41fc309b1470ff7e8565b408f697b","tid":109533,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"ust蝻亞狗呢"},{"pid":"9e2a8dd2adbcb0c9d64c33fe69633352809b6f38","tid":109533,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要召喚條垃圾ust南狗</blockquote><br />\n比佢抖下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6365eecdbd94eddd5c9694502646199b50b5f52e","tid":109533,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>受害人報警後，警方均草草了事，令惡霸有恃無恐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本就係支那有目的咁令香港由多種族社會推向所謂華人社會"},{"pid":"ea90767ac70b21670c1b0b9611a0d71e2f229886","tid":109533,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"月圓夜，南亞裔漢變「人狼」，當街非禮夜歸女被捕。現場元朗擊壤路巴士總站附近，上址經常有大批南亞裔人聚集，亦被街坊指為南亞裔人犯罪的重災區。凌晨1時許，超級月亮仍掛天邊，一名29歲女子獨自趕着歸家，途經上址時，突遭一名色膽包天南亞漢，從後突襲，涉嫌撫摸臀部非禮，事主受驚大聲呼叫，並阻止色狼離開及報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n其後，一批警員接報趕抵現場，隨即向涉案南亞色狼盤問後，以涉嫌非禮將其拘捕，被捕疑犯SYED(48歲)為印度籍，持有香港身份證，案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進，並調查他是否牽涉其他風化案。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，於上月23日晚11時許，一名南亞漢亦上址趁持「行街紙」巴籍漢與友人聊天時，突從後搶走其價值9000港元金頸鏈。警員接報截獲嫌疑男子，惟他激烈反抗逃走，警員窮追300米將其擒獲，以涉嫌襲警拘捕，被捕疑犯38歲巴籍，持有「行街紙」暫留港。"},{"pid":"a89eecb6008500b934be1dc70fe6211e72cae26a","tid":109533,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8160c3d06d3f3c14fb38c89022c1546ba33698a9","tid":109533,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ust蝻亞狗呢</blockquote><br />\n影衰我地ust <br />\n好心叫南亞狗算"},{"pid":"b511ada4d449732678e4850e615d58fe90667e00","tid":109533,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"個間乜春陳先生直頭變撚左南亞狗大使館咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70042e7f57e4d7bc417a8d661e82f2cfea730faa","tid":109533,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ust蝻亞狗呢</blockquote><br />\n召喚埋堆大愛撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野唔好一竹篙打一船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805c41f40fc7e158dac12a9302672e2453ac0c30","tid":109533,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"合益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n西菁街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2704dabf766e0675b60b4a99ee4e36728aa99db0","tid":109533,"uid":49678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逾七十歲的李婆婆，曾多次被這班男子搶手袋和<span style=\"color: red;\">非禮</span><br />\n<br />\n南亞真識食..</blockquote><br />\n土瓜灣有個比人姦埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1bed251f27081fc5e28ce65408b38392e9c147","tid":109533,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2hg69qcx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2hg69qcx&h=b0ecb933&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}